title: Katsuhiro Otomo's Memories OST
description:
Like it says, this is the soundtrack to Katsuhiro Otomo's Memories.

Note, it's not the Japanese version which is spread over 3 discs, it's the US version which is on 2 discs. As far as I can tell though, it's not missing any songs.





EDIT: Please tell me, when you copied the files into itunes, did they have all the correct info?

If not, for future reference, how can I make it so that they will?
